org.wonderly.jini.serviceui
Class PropertiesUIDemo

java.lang.Object
  org.wonderly.jini.PersistentJiniService
      org.wonderly.jini.serviceui.PropertiesUIDemo
All Implemented Interfaces:
Remote, Administrable, PropertiesAccess, RemoteAdministrable
public class PropertiesUIDemo
extends PersistentJiniService
implements PropertiesAccess, RemoteAdministrable

This is a demonstration service. It utilizes all of the convenience classes defined in this package to show how they all interact and work together. This class shows what needs to be done in other classes to have them automatically provide a ServiceUI implementation for the AdminUI so that no UI code needs to be provided by the developer. It also implements the PropertiesAccess interface and defines several properties using the Java Beans conventions of set<PropertyName> and is<PropertyName>, get<PropertyName>.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Gregg Wonderly - gregg.wonderly@pobox.com
